```
float median(float values[],int n, float&amp; median)
```
C is a little harder. For that you need a pointer:
```
float median(float values[],int n, float *median)
{
    // ...
    *median = val;
    // ...
}
// ...
find_median(output_array, row_length, &amp;median);
```

